.git
target

# Audit (2026-06-27) H-2: the Dockerfiles use `COPY . .`, so a dirty working tree would pull
# operator secrets and local state into the build context (and builder layers / cache / remote
# builder logs). Keep them out.

# Env files
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
# PQ wallet / validator seed material
**/*.kpq
**/val.seed
**/*.mnemonic
**/*.seed
# Wallet stores
**/*.wallet
**/wallet.storage
# Keys / certs
**/*.key
**/*.pem
# Known devnet key material (also in .gitignore)
**/misaka-devnet-multisig-keys.json
**/misaka-devnet-premine-key.json
# Build/dev bloat and local state
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.DS_Store
.work
.claude
analyzer-target
